function v77EvidenceTripChanged(){const t=typeof v75FindTrip==='function'?v75FindTrip($('dTrip')?.value||''):null;if(t&&$('dRoute')){$('dRoute').value=t.route||$('dRoute').value;}v77DamageSuggest(false);}
function v77SuggestType(text){const q=String(text||'').toLowerCase();for(const [type,words] of V77_DAMAGE_KEYWORDS){if(words.some(w=>q.includes(w)))return type;}return $('dType')?.value||'Scratch/Scuff';}
